 596:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_tim.c ****           Selected internal trigger is TI1F_ED.
 597:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_tim.c ****   * @note Channel 1 is configured as input, IC1 is mapped on TRC.
 598:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_tim.c ****   * @note Captured value stored in TIMx_CCR1 correspond to the time elapsed
