 601:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_tim.c ****   * @note Compare value stored in TIMx_CCR2 corresponds to the commutation delay.
 602:../../../../libs/smtc-hal-mcu-stm32l4/third_party/STM32CubeL4/Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_tim.c ****   * @note OC2REF is selected as trigger output on TRGO.
